content.rendered:
How to register your boat

Ready to register your boat?

Then go to the following addres and fill in everything there : https://www.rdw.nl/private/vehicles/vehicles/new-of-used-vessel/inschrijven-vaartuig-dat-geen-nederlandse-registratie-ha Note: you will receive your registration number by post. This will take approximately five working days.
